	(text "\nActual Product: 1987-DT024ETFT-IPS-SHB-ND\n\n3-Line 9-bit Serial Comms\n\nIM[1:0] = 01; IM1(PA9) = LOW, IM0(PA8) = HIGH\n\nUsing SPI3, RESET bound to PA2 GPIO"
